      • Vector

        public Vector(java.lang.String s,
              double xiOrNorm,
              double yiOrAngle)
        Creates an instance of Vector from cartesian or polar coordinates
        Parameters:
        s - : "cartesian" will create a vector from cartesian coordinates ; "polar" will create a vector from polar coordinates
        xiOrNorm - the x component if s is "cartesian" ; the norm if s is "polar"
        yiOrAngle - the y component if s is "cartesian" ; the angle if s is "polar"
